<v Speaker 1>Manejar.

00:07:17.300 --> 00:07:18.419
<v Speaker 2>Manejar.

00:07:18.419 --> 00:07:22.259
<v Speaker 1>And also to drive in some Latin American countries.

00:07:22.259 --> 00:07:27.300
<v Speaker 1>How would you say I am managing the problem or I manage the problem?

00:07:28.419 --> 00:07:30.419
