<v Speaker 1>So I remind you that for managing

00:07:39.440 --> 00:07:50.080
<v Speaker 1>For R verbs to get this ing we take away r and we put ando and for r ear verbs for this ing we take away the er or the ear and we put iendo

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:53.599
<v Speaker 1>First part is I am managing.

00:07:53.599 --> 00:07:56.479
<v Speaker 1>I am managing.

00:07:56.479 --> 00:07:58.560
<v Speaker 2>Stoy manejando.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.199
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:00.720
